523
00:28:52,880 --> 00:28:54,400
[SPEAKER_00] Imala sam deset minuta više za pojesti.

524
00:28:54,559 --> 00:28:56,079
[SPEAKER_01] To se ti je odlomilo i više te ispalo.

525
00:28:56,240 --> 00:28:59,119
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, sad se sjeti, ne brzo, bit ću koalen.

526
00:28:59,279 --> 00:28:59,680
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, ne, ne.

527
00:28:59,920 --> 00:29:01,200
[SPEAKER_00] Polako, skroz onako.

528
00:29:01,359 --> 00:29:02,160
[SPEAKER_00] I one to rađu.

529
00:29:05,039 --> 00:29:08,640
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, da, imamo mi stvarno vremena, ali nekako sve nas je to kužiš ubrzalo.

530
00:29:09,200 --> 00:29:11,200
[SPEAKER_00] Da, je bih, moramo se boriti.

531
00:29:13,200 --> 00:29:13,920
[SPEAKER_01] Kaznaka još.

532
00:29:14,480 --> 00:29:15,920
[SPEAKER_00] Koju muziku slušate privatno?

533
00:29:16,480 --> 00:29:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja znam da slušate sve otprilike.

534
00:29:18,720 --> 00:29:18,799
[SPEAKER_00] Sve.

535
00:29:19,359 --> 00:29:24,079
[SPEAKER_01] Trenutno ti slušam nekakav turski jazz.

536
00:29:26,160 --> 00:29:26,400
